title: Veronica's Closet
description:
These are all three seasons of this short-lived sitcom. I've been looking for it for years and finally found it on accident. Unfortunately, the quality is pretty poor (120 mb per episode), but it took me weeks to get all the files myself, so either appreciate it or provide something better. 

Also, my current upload capabilities leave a lot to be desired, so a good dose of patience will be required before you get all the files. 

Enjoy!
